data.description: Back on Market! Fantastic single story 4 bedroom with SOLAR to save on your electric bills! Open the door to a spacious entryway that leads to an open great room. Kitchen has an enormous island that looks out into the great room. This house has numerous builder upgrades: 9 foot flat ceilings, 4th bedroom option, upgraded kitchen, granite counters, over oven built in microwave, upgraded tile flooring that mimics wood floors, super bathroom package with separate garden tub and large shower, extended covered back patio, oversized  front door and french doors to back yard, extra tall garage ceiling for taller items, air purifier. Security system installed with Cox digital pad and digital thermostat. Back yard is a blank slate to make your own style.
